json > javascript object notation
(key - value) pair of data


C > Create POST
R > Read   GET
U > Update PUT
D > Delete DELETE


Params
> Send in url after /
> Need to declare in the route
> Use to small data
> Once declare in the route it is complusory to pass


QueryParams
> Send in url after ?
> No Need to declare
> use to pass multiple data
> Not complusory to pass



